在[[幾何學|幾何學]]中，'''部分截半截角八面體'''是一種[[凸多面體|凸多面體]]，是一種由[[截角八面體|截角八面體]]透過不完全的{{link-en|截半變換|Rectification_(geometry)}}而產生的一種多面體，類似於[[截半截角八面體|完全截半截角正方形鑲嵌]]，將截出來的三角形截為[[正三角形|正三角形]]，而[[截半截角八面體|完全截半截角八面體]]截出來的是[[等腰三角形|等腰三角形]]。其與[[截半截角八面體|完全截半截角八面體]]面數相同，皆為38個面，但六邊形全部被九邊形取代。

部分截半截角八面體一共有38個面、84條邊以及48個頂點，38中包含24個[[正三角形|正三角形]]、6個正方形及8個九邊形，但九邊形不是正九邊形，甚至不等角，也不等邊。但它有30個正多邊形面，已佔大部分，其在正多邊形與非正多邊形之間的物理構造上僅有非常小的差異<ref>{{citation|contribution=Symmetrohedra: Polyhedra from Symmetric Placement of Regular Polygons|title=Bridges: Mathematical Connections in Art, Music and Science|year=2001|url=http://www.cgl.uwaterloo.ca/~csk/papers/kaplan_hart_bridges2001.pdf|first1=Craig S.|last1=Kaplan|first2=George W.|last2=Hart|author2-link=George W. Hart|accessdate=2016-01-07|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923202125/http://www.cgl.uwaterloo.ca/~csk/papers/kaplan_hart_bridges2001.pdf|dead-url=no}}.</ref><ref>Joseph O’Rourke.Computational Geometry in C. Cambridge University Press, 2 edition, 1998.</ref>，因此屬於[[擬詹森多面體|擬詹森多面體]]<ref>[http://www.cgl.uwaterloo.ca/~csk/projects/nearmisses/ Near Misses] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cgl.uwaterloo.ca/~csk/projects/nearmisses/ |date=20120716191121 }} O(*,3,*,[2]) cgl.uwaterloo.ca [2016-1-7]</ref><ref>Daniele Barbaro. ''La Pratica Della Perspettiva.'' 1569. Arnaldo Forni reprint, 1980. [2016-1-8]</ref><ref>Craig S. Kaplan and George W. Hart. [http://www.cgl.uwaterloo.ca/~csk/papers/bridges2001.html Symmetrohedra: Polyhedra from Symmetric Placement of Regular Polygons] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cgl.uwaterloo.ca/~csk/papers/bridges2001.html |date=20150911003956 }}. In Bridges 2001: Mathematical Connections in Art, Music and Science, 2001.</ref>。

